	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" > <b>Copied and modified from Iriel's post</b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >In your application, include: <br />
<br />
Some info about yourself: Your character's name, level, class, magelo profile. State previous guilds you've been in, any high level alts you might have, what kind of raid experience you have, and any other personal info you think is important for us to know. State how many AAXP you have--barons do not impress us, but apps with 100+ AAs are highly desired. Also, state which kind of internet connection you have. DSL/Cable or better is HIGHLY recommended, since you must be able to stay connected and not lag on raids. You may also give some brief RL info; this seems to help people get to know you. <br />
<br />
Keys: The two keys you'll need (eventually) are the emperor key and VT key. The emp key can be completed (except for the insignia component) with a single group, and the insignia can be obtained on our emp raids. Same goes for the VT key; you'll need to obtain the 10 shards on your own or with small groups, and the rift and orb can be obtained by raiding with us. In your app, state which keys you have, or how far you are from completion of these keys. With the release of PoP, this isn't as much required, but it helps.<br />
<br />
Flags: With the PoP expansion comes the need for flags to progress through the zones. Please state which flags you have obtained. You'll need to keep up with your flags to raid with us. <br />
<br />
The essay portion of the app: <br />
-Describe how to play your class in a raid situation. <br />
-State the top three reasons you think raids fail.</font></p>
	
	<p><p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >__________________<br>
